race.description: 2026 Inglis Yearling Sale Series F&M Handicap
race.comment: SEQUISTA (8) above average filly who finally put it all together at start seven with an explosive 5.5 len win against inferior opposition over 1200m at Gosford. Placed at this trip and no shock to see her go quickly through her grades this time in. WRITTEN SCANDAL (9) just over three weeks between runs when she knocked up late in a tight finish to run third over 1250m at Randwick Kensington. Key jockey change and gets map favours. MISS BUSSLINGER (5) frustrating mare at her top here fourth-up. Trapped wide at latest when seventh over 1350m at Doomben. Ran fourth to Maid Of Moolah two-back and can surprise with Stanley's claim. Each way. CHIX (12) justified the heavy support on debut ($1.55 fav), when sat on the speed for a tough win over 1250m at Beaumont (Newcastle). Worth thought in this stronger event.
